skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Developer Terms of Use
des: This skill is the voice-activated module of Whitman County Gazette and Colfax Daily Bulletin, both based in Colfax, Wash. It will provide news headlines daily from the greater Colfax-Pullman area. To access the news from your Alexa device, you'll need to enable the skill in your Alexa app. Once enabled, it will be added to your Flash Briefing. You can access it by saying, "Alexa, what's my flash briefing," or "Alexa, what's in the news."
